name: Thumbnail for Figma
description:
Thumbnails for all your projects (personal, client, napkin-work, award-winners)! 🎉


Copy and paste "thumbnail" component into your own file to get started! 💪🏻


Select project type and change variants to suit your project! 📂


Set status variant to know your project-status at-a-glance! 👀


Plug-in the logo of the project's brand to personalise it even further! 🥳


Make it yours! 🎁
